25
00:02:40,452 --> 00:02:43,246
[zumbido, traqueteo]

26
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:46,833
[respira agitadamente]

27
00:02:46,833 --> 00:02:49,878
- [gruñidos bajos]
- [esfuerzo, gemidos]

28
